stories.text:
As a nerd, I often come up with interesting technical ideas. I would love to start writing a blog. The idea of finding someone with better writing skills than me to help me with the wording is pretty compelling.

Fiverr seems to be a big player in bringing together entrepreneurs and writers. I wonder if it is worth trying it out.

Did anybody here ever get a good blog post written on Fiverr?

If so, and you are open to link to it, that would be dope. I would love to read it.
stories.title: Ask HN: Did you get a good blog post written on Fiverr?
